---
title: Golden Chicken, Avocado & Crouton Salad with Garlic Aioli & Parmesan
description: You’re not going to believe how simple it is to make this Caesar-style salad yourself, from crunchy croutons to avocado and tender
chicken, topped with sharp Parmesan cheese. Once you’ve got this baby down, soggy supermarket salads will be a distant memory.
